    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are documented as acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Uncertainty quantification has been performed via Monte Carlo propagation yielding NIH 95th-percentile bounds that satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The planned sensitivity analysis to characterize dominant input drivers has not yet been completed, but this is judged acceptable given the medium model influence classification and the strong experimental validation results at 5 representative operating points. The overall credibility evidence supports acceptance of the CFD model for the stated COU.",
